{
  "texts": [
    "Algorithm 1 Summarizing algorithm Ranking algorithmOur novel ranking algorithm aims to assign sentence ranks according to different surface-level features.",
    "The features that we include in our system are the following:• Sentence length: The length of the sentence is directly proportional to its importance.",
    "We use sentence length as a feature for our summarizer.",
    "• Sentence Position: the position of the sentence describes its importance.",
    "The more important the sentence, the higher its position."
  ]
}